To initialize your local repository using the GeeksPhone Zero trees, use a command like this:

repo init --repo-url=git://git.omapzoom.org/tools/repo.git -u git://github.com/gpzeroDev/android.git -b gingerbread

repo sync


Configure:

choosecombo 1 1 zero 3


Compile:
make `cat /proc/cpuinfo | grep "^processor" | wc -l` "$@" otapackage


Squish:

cd vendor/geeksphone/zero/tools

./squisher

If you do this steps, you will have an update.zip file with the ROM!